ort a database, two options','en','admin',2,'2006-01-05 12:40:17'),(15055,'howto_import_huge_files_and_database','When the database and associated files reach a significant size, it is not possible to import files via a simple web form. In such circumstances, backup files must be put into the import directory (e.g. by ftp). If, additionally, the webserver can write to this directory, Lodel will offer to store backups there (backup.php). This directory is, therefore, very useful for large sites.','en','install',2,'2006-01-05 12:40:17'),(15056,'howto_index_type_1','Tag and style must contain only non-accented letters and numbers','en','admin',2,'2006-01-05 12:40:17'),(15057,'howto_index_type_2','The style defined in the text-processing program\'s Document Model may contain accented characters and spaces. Accents and spaces will be automatically removed. For example, the style \"Keyword\" in the Document Model, must be defined as \"Keyword\" here','en','admin',2,'2006-01-05 12:40:17'),(15058,'howto_index_type_3','\"Style\" may also indicate language. If this is the case, each style must be followed by \":\" and the language code. Furthermore, the styles must be separated by a comma. Example: motcle:fr, keywords:en.','en','admin',2,'2006-01-05 12:40:17'),(15059,'howto_indivdual_type_1','(*) Styles and tags may only contain non-accented characters and numbers','en','admin',2,'2006-01-05 12:40:17'),(15060,'howto_indivdual_type_2','The style defined in the text-processing program\'s Document Model may contain accented characters and spaces. Accents and spaces will be automatically removed.','en','admin',2,'2006-01-05 12:40:17'),(15061,'howto_indivdual_type_3','For example the style \"Keyword\" in the Document Model, must be defined as \"Keyword\" here','en','admin',2,'2006-01-05 12:40:17'),(15062,'howto_install_servoo_on_private_server','You can install your own ServOO server : this requires installation of OpenOffice.org and Java on your server. Such an installation requi